      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. the flight to HK sounds okay but i'm worried about the connection time. everything at the airport is just so chaotic right now with all the delays and people running around. it feels totally disorganized. are there any specific things i should look for to avoid getting stuck in more delays during a layover?",
